Here is a **Role-to-Module Mapping Table** you can include directly in your PRD, aligning actual film/series production roles with the AI-powered modules in your system:

---

### **🎬 Role-to-Module Mapping Table**

| Industry Role | Module Name | Functionality |
| ----- | ----- | ----- |
| **Storywriter** | Storywriter Module | Worldbuilding, lore, plot arcs, theme development, AI-guided storytelling prompts |
| **Scriptwriter** | Scriptwriter Module | Rich-text screenplay writing, formatting, AI suggestions, version history |
| **Showrunner** | Showrunner Module | Overall creative vision dashboard, connects and supervises all modules |
| **Director** | Director Module | Scene planning, shot breakdowns, mood boards, actor blocking, AI shot suggestions |
| **Director of Photography** | DoP Module | Lighting plans, camera setups, visual style guides, LUT previews |
| **Assistant Director (AD)** | AD Module | Scheduling, call sheets, daily breakdowns, shot priority management |
| **Production Designer** | Production Design Module | Set design, prop listing, spatial layout with references and AI visual aids |
| **Costume Designer** | Costume Module | Character costume profiles, references, AI outfit suggestions per scene |
| **Makeup Artist** | Makeup Module | Character looks, prosthetics plans, continuity tracking |
| **Sound Team** | Sound Design Module | Ambient planning, audio references, soundscape AI suggestions |
| **Composer** | Composer Module | Soundtrack planning, AI-based thematic scoring, emotion-based music suggestions |
| **Editor** | Editor Module | Timeline editor for scenes, AI pacing review, cut suggestions |
| **Colorist** | Color Module | Color grading plans, LUT previews, AI color matching for mood continuity |
| **VFX Artist** | VFX Module | VFX shot tracking, AI-based shot planning, previsualization previews |
| **Foley Artist** | Foley Module | Sound effects logging, source references, AI-assisted sync suggestion |
| **ADR Team** | ADR Module | Dialogue replacement cues, sync tools, actor note-tracking |
| **Art Director** | Art Direction Module | Visual language bible, keyframe look development, AI reference moodboards |

---

Each module is:

* 🔧 **Standalone** — Can be used independently depending on user need

* 🔗 **Interconnected** — Seamlessly integrates into the full operating system for collaborative or solo filmmaking

* 🤖 **AI-Assisted** — Offers guided questions, creative scoring, and enhancement suggestions, not just automation

