Absolutely — here’s a comprehensive list of knowledge base (KB) materials you can use for your StoryWriter Gemini agent (or in Perplexity Labs). This collection is designed to serve all skill levels (beginner to expert) and covers the core pillars of great storytelling, including:
* Story structure
* Character development
* Genre knowledge
* Writing style
* Dialogue
* Revision and editing
* Publishing tips
You can source or create these as PDFs, Markdown docs, or web references, and upload them as your agent&apos;s persistent knowledge base.
