\*\*Agentic Film/Series OS\*\*    
\# 🎬 Product Requirements Document (PRD)
\#\# 🏷️ Product Name  
\*(Temporary name — can evolve during branding)\*
\---
\#\# 📌 Overview
This is a modular, agent-powered SaaS platform that brings the entire filmmaking and series creation process into a single digital workspace. It empowers individual creators by assisting them with AI-powered modules for every creative and production role — from storywriting to post-production. AI serves not as a director, but as a question-asking assistant, guiding users through best practices while ensuring all content retains its originality and creative ownership.
\---
\#\# 🧑‍💻 Target Users
\#\#\# 👤 B2C (Phase 1\)  
\- Aspiring screenwriters  
\- Indie filmmakers  
\- YouTubers / Short-form storytellers  
\- Students in film schools  
\- Solo creators or low-budget teams
\#\#\# 🏢 B2B (Phase 2+)  
\- Film and TV studios (script development)  
\- OTT platforms (concept prototyping)  
\- Creative agencies (ideation to visualization)  
\- Media production houses
\---
\#\# 🎯 Product Vision
\&gt; “Give creative power to individuals by replacing expensive roles with intelligent AI assistance — making professional storytelling and production accessible to anyone.”
\---
\#\# 🧱 Core Philosophy
\- \*\*Modular by Design\*\*: Each module is standalone (e.g., Script Editor, Character Builder), usable independently  
\- \*\*Interconnected Ecosystem\*\*: When used together, the modules function as a complete operating system for end-to-end production  
\- \*\*AI-Guided, Human-Led\*\*: AI prompts questions and structure; user provides the original creative input  
\- \*\*&quot;Great First Draft&quot; Principle\*\*: Not a finished product generator — a creativity accelerator for beginners and pros alike
\---
\#\# ⚙️ Modules Breakdown
\#\#\# 1\. Creative Development (Pre-Production)  
| Module | Purpose |  
|--------|---------|  
| Storywriter Agent | Guides through narrative structure with AI-asked questions |  
| Scriptwriter Agent | Assists in writing screenplays (scene, dialogue, format) |  
| Character Builder | Define names, roles, arcs, relationships |  
| World Builder | Design lore: species, cultures, magic, religions |  
| Research Hub | Store articles, moodboards, and creative references |
\#\#\# 2\. Production Planning  
| Module | Purpose |  
|--------|---------|  
| Scene Breakdown | Auto-split scripts into production segments |  
| Location Manager | Tag and manage locations with metadata |  
| Casting Manager | Plan character casting with placeholders |  
| Timeline Planner | Visual production schedule with dependencies |  
| Budget Draft Tool | Basic budgeting estimates (manual or AI-aided) |
\#\#\# 3\. Post-Production Planner  
| Module | Purpose |  
|--------|---------|  
| Edit Log | Organize raw footage, notes, sequence ideas |  
| VFX Planner | Describe and mark VFX-heavy scenes |  
| Sound Design Manager | Plan ADR, Foley, original score needs |  
| Color/Grading | Describe aesthetic tone with AI examples or lookbook style references |
\#\#\# 4\. AI Assistant Capabilities  
| Feature | Description |  
|---------|-------------|  
| Questioning Agent | AI guides users via structured questions for clarity |  
| Progress Scoring | Visual feedback (e.g., character depth, pacing, tone consistency) |  
| Graphical Dashboard | Graphs of character arc density, theme evolution, scene pacing |  
| Human IP Lock | All input is by user; outputs belong to the user entirely |
\---
\#\# 🔐 Roles &amp; Permissions
| Role | Access |  
|------|--------|  
| Admin | Full access, invite collaborators |  
| Writer | Edit creative modules (story, character, etc.) |  
| Editor | Comment/edit access to scripts &amp; cuts |  
| Viewer | Read-only |  
| AI Agent | Asks questions, gives feedback, never overrides human input |
\---
\#\# 🧠 Infrastructure Plan
\- \*\*Model Source\*\*: Open-source LLMs (Mistral, Mixtral, LLaMA2, etc.) via Hugging Face  
\- \*\*Hosting\*\*: Self-hosted on private cloud GPU (e.g., RunPod, Lambda Labs)  
\- \*\*Fine-Tuning\*\*: Ongoing human-in-the-loop reinforcement learning from user interactions  
\- \*\*Storage\*\*: Encrypted media \+ structured JSON per project on scalable DB (PostgreSQL \+ S3)
\---
\#\# 🚀 Business Strategy
\#\#\# Launch Plan (B2C First)  
\- MVP release to indie creators and writers  
\- Community engagement \+ referrals  
\- Build portfolio of sample outputs from early users
\#\#\# Scale-Up Plan (B2B)  
\- Add team/project collaboration support  
\- Studio onboarding tools (bulk access, licensing)  
\- Data privacy tools for enterprise use
\---
\#\# 🧭 User Journey Snapshot (B2C)
1\. Sign up  
2\. Create a new project  
3\. AI Assistant starts asking guided questions  
4\. User answers (stored as structured data)  
5\. Modules (script, characters, etc.) auto-fill based on answers  
6\. First draft generated → user edits manually  
7\. Visual dashboards show creative consistency, progress, and insights
\---
\#\# 🧪 MVP Criteria
| Feature | Included in MVP |  
|---------|------------------|  
| Story &amp; Script Agent | ✅ |  
| Character &amp; World Builder | ✅ |  
| AI Questions \+ Input Flow | ✅ |  
| Real-Time Collaboration (2 users) | ✅ |  
| Timeline View | ❌ (Phase 2\) |  
| VFX &amp; Sound Planner | ❌ (Phase 3\) |
\---
\#\# 🏗️ Tech Stack (Initial)
| Component | Tool |  
|----------|------|  
| Frontend UI | Bubble.io / Webflow \+ custom React for advanced modules |  
| Backend Logic | Xano / Supabase |  
| Automation | Make.com |  
| AI Models | Hugging Face LLMs (self-hosted) |  
| Collaboration | Liveblocks or Yjs (React) |  
| Hosting | DigitalOcean / Render / Fly.io with GPU containers (RunPod, Modal) |
\---
\#\# 🧾 Monetization Model
| Plan | Features | Target |  
|------|----------|--------|  
| Free | 1 Project, limited modules, basic AI assistant | Students, test users |  
| Creator | Unlimited Projects, AI feedback, full creative suite | Solo users |  
| Studio | Team Collaboration, B2B dashboard, export options | Agencies, Studios |
\---
\#\# 📣 Tagline Options
\- \*\*“From Idea to Screen — Powered by You.”\*\*  
\- \*\*“Build Worlds, Not Budgets.”\*\*  
\- \*\*“Your Story. Your Draft. Our Questions.”\*\*
\---
\#\# 📝 Notes
\- This is not a fully automated storytelling engine.  
\- AI supports, the creator leads.  
\- Each interaction generates learning feedback to fine-tune the model uniquely to your user base.
